    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it's been such a great car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it! I've taken good care of it over the years, and I think you're really going to love how it handles on the road. It's the perfect balance of reliable and fun. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
